original_title: ONE Friday Fights 11: Superball vs. Kongklai 2
overview: ONE Friday Fights 11: Superball vs. Kongklai 2 was a combat sports event produced by ONE Championship that took place on March 31, 2023, at Lumpinee Boxing Stadium in Bangkok, Thailand.
